<li><a href="/wiki/Persecution_of_Jews" title="Persecution of Jews">Judaism</a>
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Antisemitism" title="Antisemitism">Antisemitism</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Anti-Judaism" title="Anti-Judaism">Anti-Judaism</a></li>
