<td><span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Flag_of_Malta.svg/23px-Flag_of_Malta.svg.png" decoding="async" width="23" height="15" class="thumbborder" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Flag_of_Malta.svg/35px-Flag_of_Malta.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/73/Flag_of_Malta.svg/45px-Flag_of_Malta.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="900" data-file-height="600" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Malta" title="Malta">Malta</a></td>
<td>1933<sup id="cite_ref-Maltese_Code_80-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Maltese_Code-80">&#91;80&#93;</a></sup></td>
<td>2016<sup id="cite_ref-Malta_repeal_82-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Malta_repeal-82">&#91;82&#93;</a></sup></td>
<td>
</td></tr>
