<td><span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/20/Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg/23px-Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg.png" decoding="async" width="23" height="15" class="thumbborder" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/20/Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg/35px-Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/20/Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg/45px-Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="900" data-file-height="600" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Netherlands" title="Netherlands">Netherlands</a></td>
<td>1886<sup id="cite_ref-Temperman620_87-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Temperman620-87">&#91;87&#93;</a></sup></td>
<td>2014<sup id="cite_ref-Temperman619_99-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Temperman619-99">&#91;99&#93;</a></sup></td>
<td>In 1932, the law was made more strict.<sup id="cite_ref-Temperman623_88-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Temperman623-88">&#91;88&#93;</a></sup>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><span class="flagicon"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Flag_of_New_Zealand.svg/23px-Flag_of_New_Zealand.svg.png" decoding="async" width="23" height="12" class="thumbborder" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Flag_of_New_Zealand.svg/35px-Flag_of_New_Zealand.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Flag_of_New_Zealand.svg/46px-Flag_of_New_Zealand.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="1200" data-file-height="600" />&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/New_Zealand" title="New Zealand">New Zealand</a></td>
<td>1893</td>
<td>2019<sup id="cite_ref-nzscoop190305_101-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-nzscoop190305-101">&#91;101&#93;</a></sup></td>
<td>The Criminal Code Act 1893 abolished and replaced the <a href="/wiki/Common_law_offences" class="mw-redirect" title="Common law offences">common law offences</a> of Blasphemy and Blasphemous libel introduced in 1840 with a code offence of Blasphemous libel.
</td></tr>
