<ul><li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1133582631"><cite id="CITEREFLanger2014" class="citation book cs1">Langer, Lorenz (2014). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=-oDRAwAAQBAJ&amp;q=lorenz%20langer%20cambridge&amp;pg=PP1"><i>Religious Offence and Human Rights: The Implications of Defamation of Religions</i></a>. Cambridge, United Kingdom: Cambridge University Press. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-107-03957-5" title="Special:BookSources/978-1-107-03957-5"><bdi>978-1-107-03957-5</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Religious+Offence+and+Human+Rights%3A+The+Implications+of+Defamation+of+Religions&amp;rft.place=Cambridge%2C+United+Kingdom&amp;rft.pub=Cambridge+University+Press&amp;rft.date=2014&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-107-03957-5&amp;rft.aulast=Langer&amp;rft.aufirst=Lorenz&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D-oDRAwAAQBAJ%26q%3Dlorenz%2520langer%2520cambridge%26pg%3DPP1&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABlasphemy+law" class="Z3988"></span></li>
